Class NativeQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.com.cybersearch2.classyjpa.query.QueryBase
      • au.com.cybersearch2.classyjpa.query.NativeQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.persistence.Query

    public class NativeQuery
extends QueryBase
    NativeQuery Implements javax.persistence.Query using native query. Only a subset of Persistence API 1.0 methods supported.
    Author:
    Andrew Bowley 30/05/2014
